          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2014-06-26T15:29:59Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Small Business Growth and Investment Act of 2014 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to increase: (1) the expensing allowance for depreciable business property to $250,000 for taxable years beginning after 2013, and (2) the threshold level for such property over which the expensing allowance is reduced to $800,000.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>]]></text>
